;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504007001: Config/Level/Mission/5040070/Act/Act504007001.json-->
::'''Dorian:''' Hello, outlander. Have you eaten yet?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not yet.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007003-->
:::'''Dorian:''' Georios says you shouldn't fight while hungry. When I'm done with work, come find me. I'll make you something to eat.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Yeah, I did. How about you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007005-->
:::'''Dorian:''' Not yet. Georios says you shouldn't fight while hungry. When I'm done with work, I'll make myself something to eat.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504007006-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007006-->
::'''Dorian:''' Now that you're here, outlander. Help me with this.
::'''Dorian:''' I caught a Dollo at three quints past the Entry Hour, and it would make great skewers. Should I roast it with salt or with sauce? Or...
::'''Camilla:''' Stop talking nonsense over there, Dorian! The direwolves are coming in!
::'''Dorian:''' Oops! Just one moment.
:;(Screen fades to black)
::A beast scurries into the city. Just as you are about to intervene, the guard swiftly deals with the intruder in a few strikes.
::Once the turmoil settles, he is immediately summoned elsewhere and only comes back after a while, looking downcast.
::'''Dorian:''' Ugh... Hmm...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Got told off?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007014-->
:::'''Dorian:''' Got told off by the captain for slacking off as a guard and not taking safety seriously. So I had to stew the Dollo for everyone to make up for it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You fought well!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007016-->
:::'''Dorian:''' Thank you. That's the basic requirement of my work. But I won't cancel out the fault that got me in trouble, so I had to stew the Dollo for everyone to make up for it.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504007017-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007017-->
::'''Dorian:''' I'm sorry, outlander. If you're hungry, I'll cook something else for you.
::'''Dorian:''' Let me introduce myself. I'm Dorian, a child of Georios. I used to be a cook, and now I'm a guard.
::'''Dorian:''' I'll be protecting Okhema, and when I'm not, I'll be cooking.
::'''Dorian:''' Now that we know each other, I won't stop you in the future anymore.
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504007002: Config/Level/Mission/5040070/Act/Act504007002.json-->
::'''Dorian:''' Nothing strange going on today.
::'''Dorian:''' Ah, it's you, outlander. Have you eaten yet?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon}} I'm starving. Got anything to eat?
:;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 304002011-->)
