:;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission not Started: 304002011-->)
:::'''Dorian:''' No, not ready yet. Come back later.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon}} I'm here for a little chat.
::'''Dorian:''' Good, I'm free now. I'm so bored that I might as well be growing mushrooms.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504007003_48-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504007003_48-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Why did you stop being a cook?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007103-->
:::'''Dorian:''' Because I didn't have a choice.
:::'''Dorian:''' I was an outlander too. When I came to Okhema, the immigration officer from the Council of Elders asked me what I did, and I told them I was a cook, and a good one.
:::'''Dorian:''' Then he scolded me, "Georios blessed you with a strong physique, but all you do is whip up meals?"
:::'''Dorian:''' They shoved armor and weapon into my hands and told me to stand here for long hours every day. But this job isn't suited for me at all.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Come on! You're pretty skilled.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007108-->
::::'''Dorian:''' I'm even more skilled in the kitchen... but they said it's not right for a Mountain Dweller to be a cook. It's a waste of my talents.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504007111-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007111-->
::::'''Dorian:''' I know, being a guard sounds more like what a Mountain Dweller should do. Plus, I can cook in secret. I can live with that.
::::'''Dorian:''' Georios made me, and I shouldn't ask for more, but it still feels bad. I want to cry. But I'm a child of Georios, and I mustn't cry.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Being a guard is a very important profession.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007110-->
::::'''Dorian:''' But cooking is important too. Like guards, cooks help keep people alive and healthy.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504007111-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007111-->
::::'''Dorian:''' I know, being a guard sounds more like what a Mountain Dweller should do. Plus, I can cook in secret. I can live with that.
::::'''Dorian:''' Georios made me, and I shouldn't ask for more, but it still feels bad. I want to cry. But I'm a child of Georios, and I mustn't cry.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
