:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504007134-->
:::'''Dorian:''' Guarding city is boring. Not much to tell.
:::'''Dorian:''' ...Trouble comes sometimes. Bad things, bad people. More bad things when I cook.
:::'''Dorian:''' My job is just to stop them, then the Chrysos Heirs and the Council of Elders take over. That's all. Guarding the city is boring.
:::'''Dorian:''' I hope I never get new stories about guarding the city.
